g.text: A customer can have at min 0 orders and at max an inifite ammount
One Order can only have one customer
One order can have one or manny Prodcuts
A prodct can be part of no or many orders
The customerid is a foregin key in the order table
so that you can know which customer made the order
In the Shipment Entity Prodct_ID and Order_NUmber are combined
to create composite Primary key, so you get a unieque value
